original_title: Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Hockey Volume 1
overview: Highlights from the 1988-89 NHL season. Narrated by Don Cherry. Don has put together the best action in hockey; hits galore, great saves, the best goals scored, plus all those funny things that happen during games. This is hockey the way 'Grapes' loves it; full of action, fun and fire!!!
title: Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Hockey Volume 1
